Today I had the regular gyro combo with seasoned fries. The gyro was very good. The meat was tender, all the veggies were fresh, and the sauce was good and in the proper amount. Fries were on point. If I had room in my stomach I would order a 2nd gyro right now and not feel bad about it.  Casual atmosphere, everyone Greek in the kitchen. Place is clean. Food came out fast.  I have nothing against Greek food at all, but I rarely seek it out. My experience here was very pleasant and I will definitely be coming back. Well done.

